-Hubbard model are very\nsensitive to the exact lattice structure, this opens up an avenue to tune\nquantum phase transitions in this solid-state system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Feb 2021 19:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Jun 2021 09:39:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-14"}
