istory of a galaxy. This is expected\nto provide a significant improvement to the accuracy of the SED fitting\noutputs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2021 06:10:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2021 08:51:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-17"}
