ion powerlaw exponent, but on the\nparameters of the transmission rate degree dependence functions, in contrast to\nordinary directed percolation and previously studied variations of the SIR\nmodel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2021 10:32:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2021 15:48:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-01"}
