 The benefit of using the covering partition oracle rather than the partition\noracle in our algorithms is its simplicity and an improved polynomial\ndependence in $1/\\epsilon$ in the obtained query complexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2021 14:42:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 May 2021 07:38:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-12"}
