\n0.973\\pm0.009\\pm0.014$, $f_{D^+_s} = 249.9\\pm2.4\\pm3.5~\\text{MeV}$, and\n$f_{D^+_s}/f_{D^+} = 1.232\\pm0.035$, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2021 14:50:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Sep 2021 12:39:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-23"}
